# User Login Troubleshooting

## Overview
One of the most common issues I have helped customers with is account access. Through my customer support and technical support experience, I learned the importance of gathering information, asking the right questions, and resolving issues quickly to get users back to work.

## Scenario 
A user was unable to access their account and received an "INVALID PASSWORD" message when attempting to log in.

## My Approach

1. Verified the user's account information.
2. Confirmed the username was entered correctly.
3. Check for common issues such as Caps Lock being enabled.
4. Verified the account was not locked or disabled.
5. Assisted the user with a password reset.
6. Tested the new credentials to confirm access.

## Resolution
The user's password was reset successfully, and access to the account was restored.

## Skills Demonstrated
- Techinical Troubleshooting
- Account Management
- Password Resets
